{"tid":221201,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[飛釘][肥仔]夏天點著先唔飛釘","createTime":"2017-04-28T13:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T14:07:00.000Z","uid":60423,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7afea0eac98502c7591cd13f1333e50456a97d5","tid":221201,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"行行下街俾女神見到我條肥毒飛釘真係霸氣盡失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知有冇咩牌子/邊類衫會唔飛釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有肥仔波真係好易飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我著過啲polo都唔錯但驚成日著會好啊叔/怪<br />\n著T裇就唔係件件都唔飛所以好難買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心口有個大公仔嘅衫就一定遮到不過男人老狗唔係咁想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知有冇咩地方/淘寶有啲淨色/得少少logo/圖案嘅簡單t，又唔會飛釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申175 80kg 肥毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe130a433a2f31a26722b8595f8cab37a1bf550","tid":221201,"uid":3577,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"又肥又毒又樣衰唔使攪咁撚多野<br />\n<br />\n冇人會留意你"},{"pid":"8dfdf2c8d5d6888201960d5140c1d5dd82be20d2","tid":221201,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又肥又毒又樣衰唔使攪咁撚多野<br />\n<br />\n冇人會留意你</blockquote><br />\n呢句真"},{"pid":"f06cf49b95707a14e3dc549c80e21649970ae434","tid":221201,"uid":49055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又肥又毒又樣衰唔使攪咁撚多野<br />\n<br />\n冇人會留意你</blockquote><br />\n呢句真</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824b92e3f07e109515e712e45dbe60b928ee0047","tid":221201,"uid":7119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:12: